ygData.messageBody:
I was trying to solo a lizard fanatic when a
train of zealots and other crud hit me...so i zone with
exactly 84 HPs remaining (i watch my HPs when i'm
low)...and end up in Freeport! I check my exp bar and it has
gone down 3/4 of a bar. ARG!!! Another bug! Ok i guess
you guys are sick of my ranting and bad fortune so
i'll stop here =p<br> - Gilerrin Galewind, Ranger of
the 31st Rank, to be stuck at this infernal lvl
forever...=\
